data.title: St. Louis AAA Blues
data.text:
We would like to start by thanking everyone for participating in our 2024/25 tryouts. We have had a record number of kids trying out across all 13 teams and appreciate the opportunity.

Please select the appropriate team by birthyear for current tryout results.

We are listing the player's by number and if your number is on the list, please report to the next skate.

We are excited to announce our tryout schedule and registration link for the 2024-25 season.

Please see below for general tryout information and then click on specific birthyear for additional details including dates, times, etc.

WHERE: Centene Community Ice

WHEN: May 15th thru May 23rd (click each birth year for details below)

COST: $85 tryout fee (bring dark and light jersey)

HOW: Please click the link below for registration or top right of the page
